@scheduleIdAbmael = 3187a57a-518b-4d9d-8b03-df03f12efe49
@scheduleIdAbmaelInexistente = gc3a020d-aad1-4950-9bf5-ba1865c5431h

### [SUCESSO] Atualizar horário existente
# Esperado: 200 com horário atualizado
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/schedules/{{scheduleIdAbmael}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dayOfWeek": "tuesday",
  "startTime": "07:00",
  "endTime": "13:00"
}

###

### [SUCESSO] Atualizar mantendo mesmo horário (sem conflito consigo mesmo)
# Esperado: 200 — o próprio registro é ignorado na checagem de conflito
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/schedules/{{scheduleIdAbmael}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dayOfWeek": "monday",
  "startTime": "07:00",
  "endTime": "13:00"
}

###

### [FALHA] Atualização gera conflito com outro horário existente
# Esperado: 400 
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/schedules/{{scheduleIdAbmaelInexistente}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dayOfWeek": "monday",
  "startTime": "07:00",
  "endTime": "13:00"
}

###

### [FALHA] Atualização gera conflito com outro horário existente
# Esperado: 409 ConflictError
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/schedules/{{scheduleIdAbmael}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dayOfWeek": "monday",
  "startTime": "10:00",
  "endTime": "16:00"
}

###

### [FALHA] dayOfWeek ausente no body
# Esperado: 422 Validation Error com campo dayOfWeek nos issues
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/schedules/{{scheduleIdAbmael}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startTime": "09:00",
  "endTime": "17:00"
}

###

### [FALHA] startTime >= endTime
# Esperado: 422 Validation Error com campo startTime nos issues
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/schedules/{{scheduleIdAbmael}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dayOfWeek": "monday",
  "startTime": "17:00",
  "endTime": "09:00"
}

###

### [FALHA] Sem token de autenticação
# Esperado: 401 UnauthorizedError
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/schedules/{{scheduleIdAbmael}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dayOfWeek": "tuesday",
  "startTime": "08:00",
  "endTime": "12:00"
}

###
